Package: gapAPI
Type: Package
Title: GAP API interface
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-06-24
Author: Matthew Upson
Maintainer: <ivyleavedtoadflax@gmail.com>
Description: Package of wrapper functions (based mainly on httr) which facilitate access to the GAP REST API (https://developer.globalalerting.com/API) for downloading GPS data from tracking units. It is primary intended for the downloading of Cattle GPS data.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    httr (>= 0.6.1),
    jsonlite,
    lubridate,
    readr,
    RCurl (>= 1.95-4.6),
    XML (>= 3.98-1.1),
    magrittr


